short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replaces 2016 US presidential candidates' names with 'Jeb Bush.'

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The 2016 US Presidential Election can be exciting, but it can be depressing. It's so sad seeing the electoral field without our most beloved candidate, Jeb Bush. Make America Jeb Again. Put Jeb back on the web. Replace every other candidate's name with "Jeb Bush." Please clap.
